-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- File       : AmcCarrierTiming.vhd
-- Company    : SLAC National Accelerator Laboratory
-- Created    : 2015-07-08
-- Last update: 2017-11-03
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Description: 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
